profile:
Personalize your home and let its appearance reflect your lifestyle, interests and ideals by availing topnotch residential painting in Sudbury from Majic Colours Painting Services. Our experienced and professional painters will work according to your specifications and they only utilize high quality painting materials and products from the leaders of the industry.

Despite our professionalism and penchant for perfection, we see to it that we work according to our clients’ boundaries. We respect your parameters so even if we think your house would look grand in pastel colors, if you prefer it in earthly hues, we’ll execute the job according to your preference. No questions asked.

Aside from putting greater weight on what you like for your home, we’re also proud to say that we offer our services at prices you can definitely reach. We’re not out to match our first-class service with soaring rates. As homeowners ourselves, we understand how difficult it is to find a company these days that has a heart. With us, that is what you’ll get.

To get a free estimate on residential and commercial painting, drywall installation and repair, or affordable parging for your masonry structures, contact us at 705-920-6029.

Majic Colours Painting Services is happy to be of service to you anywhere in Sudbury.

If you're looking for someone to paint one door, or paint your entire home, then I hope you give us a try. On every job we try to exceed the expectations of the customer through our commitment to perfection, quality and high standards.

Your home is your most valuable asset. A fresh coat of paint will make it look great and keep it protected for years to come. SD Paint & Design offers comprehensive residential / commercial, interior / exterior painting services from start to finish. We make your painting experience hassle-free with our FREE Colour consultation, precise job management, and fully insured Crew. Our painting crew will be respectful of your home, while providing the best service you will find in the area. Our teams are knowledgeable, friendly, and will be there to answer every question you have along the way to make sure you are 100% satisfied.

We also provide a wide range of renovation and construction services to residential customers in and around the North Bay area. It is always refreshing to have a service provider going that extra mile to deliver continued work satisfaction. Our team includes experienced, skilled, and qualified tradesmen and we guarantee 100% professional quality service. Our crew is dedicated to our work and to our clients. We aim to provide quality service. We offer appropriate and fair cost, a superior quality and we will work hard to fit your schedule and complete all projects in a timely manner. It is our goal to satisfy our customers and to ensure that you will continue to use our services as part of keeping your home as livable as possible.

Seniors Discount – Contractors pricing available – Rental Unit Discounts
